com.dropbox.core.v2.team

Class ResendSecondaryEmailResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dropbox.core.v2.team.ResendSecondaryEmailResult

  • public final class ResendSecondaryEmailResult
extends java.lang.Object
    Result of trying to resend verification email to a secondary email address. 'success' is the only value indicating that a verification email was successfully sent. The other values explain the type of error that occurred, and include the email for which the error occured.

    This class is an open tagged union. Tagged unions instances are always associated to a specific tag. This means only one of the isAbc() methods will return true. You can use tag() to determine the tag associated with this instance.

    Open unions may be extended in the future with additional tags. If a new tag is introduced that this SDK does not recognized, the OTHER value will be used.
